{"tid":2420160,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無發覺啲人唔食西芹 芹菜 芫茜是但一個，就其餘兩個都唔會食?","createTime":"2021-02-23T17:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T19:16:01.000Z","uid":199697,"like":25,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c607b2f5cd2c19414062f0f3b01e9e1099caea","tid":2420160,"uid":199697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"話說嗰陣喺宿舍，見雪櫃有幾個蕃茄薯仔就諗住整埋一齊煲個湯飲下，咁梗係要落啲西芹吊下味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點知我一拎棵西芹，我個roommate聞到陣味即刻反晒胃作嘔<br />\n咁好啦，我唔落西芹，芫荽得喇掛? 點知佢又屌我話芫荽好撚臭，問我係咪食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我就咁整蕃茄肉片湯就算，但無西芹芫荽真係差噉啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我問幾個唔食芫荽嘅fd，發現佢哋都好憎西芹同芹菜，有無巴打都發現依個現象?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 好撚鐘意芫茜西芹，有時煮完嘢仲會dump一大堆芫茜落去，好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2016.05/2016.05.13/Parsley/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2016.05%2F2016.05.13%2FParsley%2F1.jpg&h=1e035c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8cf4dc8b9f2bc5685267117d44f03fd66b1adb","tid":2420160,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"我食西芹, 雖然唔係好鍾意嗰隻<br />\n唔食臭茜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4d1302ff32594662227448fd2dcfb395d4eb75","tid":2420160,"uid":287879,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"我都唔食呢3樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce723c5ee5de8e035250d1ccd37777b010f5d4a","tid":2420160,"uid":388055,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"我三樣都會食<br />\n三樣都係差唔多"},{"pid":"e3cb8dc8462b799398f025d9a14f9d19406d5806","tid":2420160,"uid":199697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca4d1302ff32594662227448fd2dcfb395d4eb75","tid":2420160,"uid":287879,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"我都唔食呢3樣野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"西芹芹菜陣味可以話差唔多<br />\n但明明芫茜同佢哋陣味都幾唔同下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解巴打唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda54f5c10285500e7deb5b5d97689674982d2da","tid":2420160,"uid":72633,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"勁食芫荽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔鍾意食西芹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c26d3466bcf2a1847d92308f459a29c437748a6","tid":2420160,"uid":211578,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"食芫茜但唔食西芹同芹菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59efff43ac10efd57efcc138962d13ee5f7e9a33","tid":2420160,"uid":1903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:42:43.000Z","msg":"真 全部都唔食"},{"pid":"44daf252a7b3e7b660557702d7485a662bd811b3","tid":2420160,"uid":287879,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e3cb8dc8462b799398f025d9a14f9d19406d5806","tid":2420160,"uid":199697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca4d1302ff32594662227448fd2dcfb395d4eb75","tid":2420160,"uid":287879,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20